## Question

Which popular Chrome extension categories should inform Turing's first-party maintained Plug-ins, and what architecture avoids inheriting the extension ecosystem's security, privacy, performance, and maintenance failures?

## Method and limits

The study recorded a twenty-item reference cohort from public Chrome Web Store pages on 2026-07-16. Selection used rounded store user counts plus category coverage. It is not claimed as an exact global top-20 ranking, because store counts are dynamic and popularity is not equivalent to quality, safety, retention, or performance.

